					<div id="mw-content-text" lang="de" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><figure class="thumb tright thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="http://images.rychu.wikia-dev.com/__cb20060821123758/de.gta/images/4/41/Chaos-Derby_Banger.JPG" class="image"><img alt="Chaos-Derby Banger" src="http://images.rychu.wikia-dev.com/__cb20060821123758/de.gta/images/thumb/4/41/Chaos-Derby_Banger.JPG/180px-Chaos-Derby_Banger.JPG" width="180" height="135" class="thumbimage" data-image-name="Chaos-Derby Banger.JPG" data-image-key="Chaos-Derby_Banger.JPG" /></a><a href="/wiki/Datei:Chaos-Derby_Banger.JPG" class="internal sprite details magnify" title="Zeige Bild-Informationen"></a><figcaption class="thumbcaption">Chaos-Derby Banger, Downtown<div class="picture-attribution"><img src="http://images.rychu.wikia-dev.com/__cb2/common/avatars/thumb/8/80/34444.png/20px-34444.png" width="16" height="16" class="avatar" alt="Zaibatsu" />Hinzugefügt von <a href="/wiki/Benutzer:Zaibatsu">Zaibatsu</a></div></figcaption></figure>
<p>Die <b>Chaos-Derby-Banger</b> <i>(engl. <b>Bloodring Banger</b>)</i> sind zwei Stockcars aus <a href="/wiki/Grand_Theft_Auto:_Vice_City" title="Grand Theft Auto: Vice City">Grand Theft Auto: Vice City</a>, deren Modelle auf dem <a href="/wiki/Glendale_(VC)" title="Glendale (VC)">Glendale</a> und dem <a href="/wiki/Oceanic_(VC)" title="Oceanic (VC)">Oceanic</a> basieren. Als reales Vorbild dient der 1958er <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/de:Dodge_Coronet" class="extiw" title="wikipedia:de:Dodge Coronet">Dodge Coronet</a>.
</p>
